## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="412bf-109">O código c# a seguir usa `GetNode` para acessar um nó de <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> está atualmente posicionado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="412bf-109">The following C# code uses `GetNode` to access a node the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is currently positioned on.</span></span>  

```csharp  
XmlDocument doc = new XmlDocument();  
doc.Load("books.xml");  
XPathNavigator nav =  doc.CreateNavigator();  
XmlNode node = ((IHasXmlNode)nav).GetNode();  
Console.WriteLine(node.LocalName);   
//You can edit the returned XmlNode.  
```
